Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Year 845.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The Colossal Titan and the Armored Titan appeared out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Instantly, the walls were shattered, along with the illusory peace of everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, driven by a century of hunger, the Titans
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,descended upon mankind once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.88,0:00:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind abandoned Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.28,0:00:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They lost a fifth of their population, and a third of their territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,as human activity was pushed back to Wall Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You're slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.49,0:02:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Run, you shitheads!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Arlert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're falling behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.67,0:02:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it too hard for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be the only one who puts down his equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.67,0:02:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If this was a real mission, you'd be Titan food already!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Give that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.97,0:02:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll end up dropping out this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're being graded on today's training!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, they're gonna punish you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do your best so they won't find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.07,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me change my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiner Braun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,He possesses great mental and physical fortitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,His comrades trust him deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than live as a burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Armin Arlert.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What he lacks in physical strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.79,0:03:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,he makes up for with extraordinary academic aptitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.61,0:03:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie Leonhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,While her fighting skills are outstanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,she doesn't work well as part of a team. A lone wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bertolt Hoover.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He is highly talented, but he lacks initiative.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean Kirstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,His 3D control skills are top class,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but his overtly blunt personality causes friction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fight like them. I need to find my own Titan first!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} get accepted into the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Jean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.63,0:04:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew following you would work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha Blouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's talented at operating unconventionally,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but that mentality makes her unfit for organized activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Connie Springer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He's skilled at making sharp turns, but his mind is nowhere near sharp enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! I still didn't cut deep enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikasa Ackerman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Her performance is exemplary in every subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.71,0:05:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She is truly a genius of historically-unprecedented significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,While he lacks any outstanding talents, he improved his grades through outstanding diligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, he possesses an exceptional sense of purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.72,0:05:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.09,0:05:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I suck at holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You play the bad guy next.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't see the point of training like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like soldiers fight other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, only a fool would go bare-\Nhanded against an armed opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's irresponsible thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There are times we can't back down, no matter how hopeless the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't always be sure who or what we're up against,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,so we master artillery and hand-to-hand combat too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our responsibility as soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Would ya look at that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The officers never notice her sneaking off like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's teach that slacker a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show her how true soldiers ought to behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You looking for a headbutt from the instructor?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.99,0:06:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna get any shorter, I suggest you recall your first day here and get serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've always thought she wore a scary face,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but that's nothing compared to right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get moving, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie, you know what to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She kicked me in the leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.92,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It's not over until he lets go of the dagger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Annie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.72,0:07:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to do it the way—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's your turn to attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Reiner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:07:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna teach her the responsibility of being a soldier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Sometimes a soldier can't back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.09,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Like right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your technique is incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.32,0:08:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Who taught you to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father could—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.98,0:08:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing this is pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean this training?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.78,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anti-personnel techniques don't factor into our scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.37,0:08:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So people just take it easy until it's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The right to join the Military Police and live in the secure Inner District
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,is only granted to the top scoring 10 graduates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The people who bother participating in this are either stupidly serious like you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,or seriously stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap, it's the instructor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in this world are the people most capable of opposing the Titans
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.08,0:09:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the only ones given the privilege of avoiding them entirely?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you think it got to be such a farce?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just human nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Point is, I can't even pretend to be stupid \Nenough to play soldier in this insane world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you're not fit to be a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was so obsessed with getting stronger that I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's such an obvious contradiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're just improving their Titan-killing skills so they have a chance to get further away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the fall of Wall Maria,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,only the few soldiers of the Recon Corps actually utilized the 3D Maneuver Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,With limited usage or innovation, the entire practice would naturally fall into decline...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You should rev it up hard, but just for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Using inertia that way, you can minimize gas consumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You make it sound so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's not something anyone could master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still worth remembering
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're trying to get into the Military Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if I could get in...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no higher honor than working near the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Marco!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being such a goody-goody and just tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to join the Military Police so you can live a simple, comfortable life within the Inner District.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I actually want to—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So interior life's simple and comfortable?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years ago, this place was also part of the interior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your point, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.39,0:11:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Jean, you're such a simpleton, you'd be comfortable wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Learning how to kill Titans just to run away from them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You bring that up now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.68,0:11:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This farce should be kept going for my sake if nothing else!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck off and face reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you! I backed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.83,0:11:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares! I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you even talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just blowing off steam, just like I did back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use my skills to resolve the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.04,0:12:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a move I learned while you were slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think reality is just living comfortably and following your own whims,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,can you seriously dare to call yourself a soldier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I just heard some kind of loud noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone care to enlighten me as to what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha just ripped a giant fart, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn some self-control!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus the graduation of the 218 trainees drew near.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.81,0:13:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hands upon your hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For you trainees graduating today, three paths now open before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You can be stationed at the walls and defend the cities as members of the Garrison!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put your lives on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to fight the Titans in their own territory as members of the Recon Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can serve the King by controlling the crowds and protecting order
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,as members of the Military Police Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.79,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, only the ten people with top scores we \Nannounced earlier are allowed into the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally, I made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, it'll be our turn
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to devour the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it! I'm in the Military Police now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never worry about having food again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I below Eren? That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna join the Military Police, Eren? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've got one of the top 10 scores!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been dead-set on my goal since the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.61,0:14:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't train to live comfortably within the Inner District.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked this hard so that I could fight the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.61,0:14:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't possibly win!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You know full well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know just how many have been eaten by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost more than twenty percent of the entire population already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind doesn't stand a chance against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just giving up because you think you can't win?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.33,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true. We've suffered only defeats so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because we knew hardly anything about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.05,0:15:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't defeat them using sheer numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We may have lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,but the knowledge we obtained from those battles is our guiding beacon of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.63,0:15:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet you'd discard the tactical progress bought by hundreds of thousands of sacrifices,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.01,0:15:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,just to serve yourself up on a silver platter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill every last one of them and break free of these walls!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That is my dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind hasn't lost everything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:15:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go outside those walls, if you're so keen on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to the Military Police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:16.37,Default,,0,0,100,,Eren, can we talk about your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.37,0:16:17.35,Default,,0,0,100,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.03,Default,,0,0,100,,After all, I got it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.20,Default,,0,0,100,,Breaking free of the walls, and all that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:25.84,Default,,0,0,100,,I'm going to enlist in the Recon Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.66,Default,,0,0,100,,Are you for real, Armin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.66,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,100,,You're our top theoretician! Put that to better use!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:34.34,Default,,0,0,100,,I don't care if I die as long as I can be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:37.60,Default,,0,0,100,,I'm going to the Recon Corps too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.22,Default,,0,0,100,,You got the top score, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.69,Default,,0,0,100,,Go to the military police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:46.48,Default,,0,0,100,,I'll go to the military police if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.24,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,100,,If you go to the Garrisons, so will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die an early death \Nif I'm not there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I never asked for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to lose what's left of my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The main force of the Recon Corps is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Commander Erwin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick their Titan asses for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.10,0:17:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Commander Levy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.65,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They say he alone counts for a full unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can they shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They look completely different from five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,People really count on the Recon Corps a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cheering everyone up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The past won't have to be repeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The artillery has been improved as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That Colossal Titan won't come again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so naive, you old married couple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call us a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so hasty, Eren.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.86,0:18:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hannes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.36,0:18:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys graduated yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.46,0:18:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they really let you kids through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they made a drunkard like you Captain of a Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Touché!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.74,0:18:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't save your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault, Hannes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no longer ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let that sort of tragedy happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I will defeat the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.65,0:18:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I be happy or not that he's grown into a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.09,0:18:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just don't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You enlisted in the Recon Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Connie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.05,0:19:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You were going on and on about joining the Military Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.49,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like he was listening to your lecture yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.42,0:19:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my own decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so shy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thomas...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.95,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I borrowed some meat from the officers' morning rations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.37,0:19:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna get solitary confinement?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Real idiocy's scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.36,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all split it up together later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll slice it up and eat it with bread!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.32,0:19:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Meat is a luxury now that we've lost so much land!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we retake the land, we can keep pigs and cows again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take that meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too, so save my part!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.43,0:20:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.78,0:20:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Eren?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll find us out if we don't get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still a while before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Five years have passed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's finally regaining its dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's counterattack begins now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.23,0:21:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Samuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Samuel! Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.24,0:21:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The gate's... broken...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Again... The Titans will get in again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.83,0:21:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll kill them all! Every single one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Every... fucking... one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready the artillery! Four groups!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.45,0:21:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.17,0:22:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The target's right in front of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.51,0:22:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Colossal Titan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our chance! Don't let it slip away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 5 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.83,0:23:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell's gates have opened once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.56,0:24:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even time to catch their breath, soldiers are consumed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Amidst the chaos, Armin stares death in the face. Can Eren save him?
