Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.72,0:01:09.10,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Prayers won't save us
Dialogue: 1,0:01:09.02,0:01:14.58,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Only the will to fight can change our world
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.28,0:01:16.86,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Ignore those pigs who ridicule you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.66,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}for having the will to step over dead bodies and move on
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.46,0:01:22.38,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Our complacence as livestock strengthens this false reality
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.12,0:01:25.10,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}We're as free as starving wolves!
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.94,0:01:30.50,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Channel the humiliation of imprisonment into your fists and fight the oppression
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.22,0:01:35.72,Op TL,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,25)\blur2\fad(200,200)}Far beyond the confining walls, you'll slay your prey!
